BobUI 3.3.7 is a bug-fix release. It maintains both forward and backward
compatibility (source and binary) with BobUI 3.3.6, 3.3.5, 3.3.4, BobUI 3.3.3,
BobUI 3.3.2, BobUI 3.3.1 and BobUI 3.3.0.

****************************************************************************
*                           General                                        *
****************************************************************************

- QImage
        Fixed a potential security issue which could arise when transforming
        images from untrusted sources.

